summary: so I drew it about 4 months ago. it is actually the first art I've ever drawn on MY OWN graphic tablet and although it's not...
body:
so I drew it about 4 months ago. it is actually the first art I’ve ever drawn on MY OWN graphic tablet and although it’s not perfect at all, I really am proud of myself

(but I think it’s because Brie Larson is perfect even if she was drawn by such beginner as me)

I’ve upload it to my twitter because I don’t use Tumblr really often but while I’m here I have to upload it to Tumblr too (idk why I just want to)

hope you like it💕
